text: James Murphy (29 September 1911 - 7 May 1984) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales in 1938/39. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1911 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: James Murphy (cricketer)
